  "Means root": [
   {
    "text": "The word shoresh can mean “root” or “source.” ",
    "type": "text"
   },
   {
    "topLevelNodes": [
     {
      "ordinal": "-",
      "ordered": false,
      "tokensOfLine": [
       {
        "text": "In this context, it means “root” in the sense that a words like “memory” and “memorize” come from the same linguistic root “mem.”",
        "type": "text"
       }
      ],
      "children": []
     }
    ],
    "type": "outline"
   }
  ],
  "Generally have three letters, but may sometimes have two or four letters": [
   {
